<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘和皮特陷入了困境。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘，回到我的房子里去！”格雷夫人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“斯利姆吗？下来！”洛夫斯先生大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生，求您了。”拇指姑娘央求道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只鸟是我的朋友。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生挥了挥他的拐杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经答应斯利姆了，我是个信守诺言的人。”他坚定的说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回去穿上你的婚纱，拇指姑娘。”格雷夫人看了看她的手表，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上要到婚礼的时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会嫁给他的！”拇指姑娘大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人突然看见了地上的婚纱，上面布满了食物和泥土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘，那是你的婚纱吗？”她惊讶地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抓起了婚纱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“婚纱都被毁了！你还把我的食物都给这只鸟了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，真是浪费时间。”鼹鼠嘟囔道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“反正斯利姆马上就要吃掉他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>忽然一个毛茸茸的大爪子从洞口伸了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只鸟闻起来还活着，洛夫斯！更好！”斯利姆吼叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特盯着头顶那只毛茸茸的尖爪子，吓呆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘必须马上想出对策。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼马上就要从洞口爬进来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然拇指姑娘想出了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始给皮特唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皮特， 听我唱。”她开始唱了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊？什么？”皮特盯着拇指姑娘，他看起来很困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你从哪里学的那首歌？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘记得克里斯和麦琪教的可以和鸟儿秘密对话的歌曲，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始唱道：“我会挥起婚纱，那只狼会被迷惑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后你马上往上飞，我拉住你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太危险了。”皮特唱到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么能在这个时候唱歌？”格雷夫人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她确实有一副好嗓音。”洛夫斯先生叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用拐杖随着歌声打拍子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘又开始唱那首歌。她边唱边盯着皮特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确定吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能做到！”拇指姑娘唱道 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，皮特！”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘从格雷夫人手里夺过婚纱，在空中挥动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坚果和种子在空气中飞扬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些坚果打到老鼠和鼹鼠的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎哟！”他们大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘松开了婚纱，风把婚纱带了起来，吹向斯利姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于可以吃了！”斯利姆好像饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他咬住了裙子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皮特！”拇指姑娘大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特展开翅膀，直飞向洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘抓住了他的腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊？什么？这不是一只鸟！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>斯利姆意识到自己错了，但是已经太迟了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘！”格雷夫人和洛夫斯从地道里大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的晚餐！”斯利姆跳着大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>